        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 17 at 4:38PM MDT until July 17 at 5:15PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 437 PM MDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 8 miles southwest of Chester to 11 miles southeast of
Lothair to 18 miles north of The Knees, moving southeast at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Chester and Tiber Dam.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
